<%- include("../modules/header.ejs", {
    pageTitle: pageTitle,
    pageDescription: "Support Crafting For Christ and keep the network growing."
}) %>

<%- include("../modules/navigationBar.ejs") %>

<%- include("../partials/miniHeader.ejs", {
  headerTitle: "Support the Server",
  backgroundImage: globalImage
}) %>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mb-5 text-center">
      <h2>🙏 Support Crafting For Christ</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Crafting For Christ is a Minecraft network built around faith, friendship, and fun.
        Your support helps keep the servers online and the community growing.
      </p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <a href="/ranks" class="btn btn-outline-primary">See Ranks &amp; Perks</a>
        <a href="/webstore" class="btn btn-primary">Support the Server</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <h3>✨ Why We Ask for Support</h3>
      <p>Running Minecraft servers costs money every month. Your support helps pay for things like:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Server hosting</li>
        <li>Backups and security</li>
        <li>Plugins and updates</li>
        <li>Events and new features</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Our goal is to keep Crafting For Christ a safe, positive, Christ-centred place for everyone to enjoy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <h3>💰 This Month’s Server Goal</h3>
      <p>Each month we have a set goal to cover our server costs.</p>
      <div class="progress mb-2" style="height: 24px;">
        <div
          class="progress-bar"
          role="progressbar"
          style="width: <%= progressPercent %>%"
          aria-valuenow="<%= progressPercent %>"
          aria-valuemin="0"
          aria-valuemax="100"
        >
          <%= progressPercent %>% funded
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-muted">
        <strong>$<%= (raisedCents / 100).toFixed(2) %></strong>
        of <strong>$<%= (monthlyGoalCents / 100).toFixed(2) %></strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted">Every purchase or donation through the store helps move this bar forward.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <h3>💬 How You Can Help</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Buy a Rank</strong>
          <p>Ranks help support the server and give you cool in-game perks.</p>
          <a href="/ranks">View ranks here</a>
        </li>
        <li class="mt-3">
          <strong>Monthly Support</strong>
          <p>You can also support the server monthly if you want to help long-term.</p>
          <a href="/webstore">Support or gift here</a>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">You can even gift a rank to another player to bless them!</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <h3>❤️ What Your Support Does</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep the servers running smoothly</li>
        <li>Create a safe place to play</li>
        <li>Encourage faith and kindness</li>
        <li>Welcome new players</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Crafting For Christ isn’t just a server — it’s a community where people can grow together.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <h3>📢 Server Updates</h3>
      <p>
        This section is used for important updates, like server upgrades, maintenance times, or big changes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted">(Updates will appear here when needed.)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <h3>🙏 Thank You for Being Here</h3>
      <p>Thank you for playing, praying, and supporting Crafting For Christ.</p>
      <p class="text-muted">“Whatever you do, do it all for the glory of God.” ❤️</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("../modules/footer.ejs") %>
